  SELECT gen_random_uuid()::text, e.id, $patch$You are configuring a new firewall appliance for your company's network. Internal Windows servers must be able to retrieve the latest updates over the Internet. Which egress port must you allow through your firewall?$patch$, 'SINGLE'::"QType", $patch$[{"id":"A","text":"Ports 23 and 25"},{"id":"B","text":"Ports 20 and 21"},{"id":"C","text":"Ports 80 and 443"},{"id":"D","text":"Ports 389 and 636"}]$patch$::jsonb, $patch$["C"]$patch$::jsonb, $patch$Correct Answer: Ports 80 and 443 is correct. Windows Update retrieval over the Internet uses TCP ports 80 and 443.$patch$, $patch$Security and Disaster Recovery$patch$, 3, $patch$[{"url":"https://www.comptia.org/certifications/server","label":"CompTIA Server+ exam objectives"}]$patch$::jsonb, 'DRAFT'::"QStatus", 'manual:sk0-005-prior-topup', false, NOW(), NOW()
